text: Admiralteysky, Admiralteyskaya or Admiralteyskoye may refer to: ==Places== * Admiralteysky District, a district of Saint Petersburg, Russia * Admiralteysky Municipal Okrug, a municipal okrug of Admiralteysky District of Saint Petersburg, Russia * Admiralteyskaya (Saint Petersburg Metro), a station of the Saint Petersburg Metro, Saint Petersburg, Russia * Admiralty Embankment (Admiralteyskaya naberezhnaya), a street along the Neva River in Saint Petersburg, Russia ==See also== * Admiralty (disambiguation) * Novo- Admiralteysky Bridge, a planned bridge in Saint Petersburg, Russia
title: Admiralteysky
